			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>As part of upgrading my video and audio kit to broadcast quality, I invested in a FlashMic. I had to take a deep intake of breath before buying the beast but so far it has been worth every penny.</p>
<p>Since getting it I have made about 20 audio interviews with teachers, senior leaders and with others in unrelated projects as well as lending it out to others for the <a href="http://www.youtube.com/user/DigitameVideo#p/a/u/1/MSNmK1W6Fk4">ImagineProject </a>.</p>
<p><img alt="" src=" http://farm7.static.flickr.com/6192/6152715641_1f3a2dd15e.jpg" title="L4L FlashMic" class="alignnone" width="500" height="333" /></p>
<p>It has definitely increased my productivity and workflow and the sound is superb. </p>
