			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><iframe src="http://blip.tv/play/gr5HgtObIgA.html" width="500" height="300" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe><embed type="application/x-shockwave-flash" src="http://a.blip.tv/api.swf#gr5HgtObIgA" style="display:none"></embed></p>
<p>Will be researching/ filming over the next year for a 2013 release&#8230;</p>
<p>Realistically it will take me about 18 months &#8211; as well as documenting the history of TeachMeet and interviewing all the key players in the UK &#8211; I am looking for 3 &#8211; 4 teachers who plan to go to a teachmeet for the very first time. I&#8217;d be interested in documenting their reactions to the process. </p>
<p>I&#8217;ll be using broadcast quality equipment.  Please get in touch if you know anyone who would like to help. </p>
