<p>My audioBoo interview with <a title="Link to Theo's excellent site" href="http://theok.typepad.com/" target="_blank">Theo Kuechel</a> for the <a title="#purposedfutured link" href="http://purposed.org.uk/2011/05/announcing-the-next-campaign-purposedfutured/" target="_blank">#purposedfutured</a> campaign.</p>
<p>Theo was kind enough to step in at  the very last minute and give his answers to the two questions:</p>
<p>A) How should we educate people in the future?</p>
<p>B) What do we need to be doing now to enable that?</p>
<p>His response was typically pertinent, highly creative and very amusing.</p>
