			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I have filmed so many conversations at BETT2011 that I have decided to put up a dedicated <a href="http://www.l4l.co.uk/?page_id=240" target="_blank">TV channel</a> to the content. Of course there is so much content it will take me weeks to get it out.</p>
<p>So I have decided to devote an area of this site to the films and live video feeds as they happen over the year. I do so many of them now I feel all those marvellous conversations would be wasted if there wasn&#8217;t a smart way to put the information up in manageable packets.</p>
<p>So here&#8217;s a quick preview of the service I&#8217;m going to be rolling out for free in the next few weeks&#8230;.</p>
<p>I hope, as usual, people find these ideas useful:</p>
